productBaseInfoV1.title: MBOX 300 lm DLP Corded & Cordless Mobiles Portable Projector(Black)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: •Intelligent, small, lightweight and versatile. AODIN T89 is a feature packed palm sized Android DLP projector compatible with both iPhone and Android devices. With 5G WiFi, auto vertical keystone correction, HDMI, Bluetooth and 32GB of inbuilt storage, enjoy seamless internet streaming and ample space for all your movies, video games, presentations and media. •AODIN T89’s Android interface comes pre-loaded with a host of entertainment and business apps including Netflix, Hulu, HBO, YouTube, Polaris Office and Google Drive. Can't find an app? Download it from Google Play Store app direct from the device. Simply switch T89 on, select your app and enjoy fast lag free projection. Want to mirror your mobile phone display instead? With Airplay and Miracast apps preloaded screen mirroring is quick and easy. •With 1500 lumens (300 Ansi), 2000:1 contrast ratio, crisp 854x480p native resolution and screen projection size up to 120 inches, cuddle up in bed and stream the latest Netflix show onto the ceiling, impress your dorm buddies or delight the kids with their favorite Disney movie while you put your feet up! •With our 1080p compatible HDMI Input feature, connect any HDMI friendly device such as your Xbox One, PlayStation or laptop for fast and convenient screen projection. With vertical keystone correction the T89 will auto adjust the viewing angle to ensure a symmetric display up to +/- 45 degrees. •With a folding wireless mouse, soft carry case, expandable pivot tripod, HDMI cable, USB/DC charger cable, USB/USB data transfer cable and rechargeable battery offering 2 hours+ of unplugged play time, take the T89 anywhere. Your next family camping trip? Backyard movie night? Overnight business travel? It only weighs 230 grams so slip it in the bag. T89 comes with 1 year warranty for parts and labor.

productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Add a mini printer to any micro-controller project with this very cute thermal printer. Just send data to it serially and it will print it. It differentiates your Laptop from others. A Skin Protects Laptop from outside, adds Aesthetic Appeal and make it Stand Out from the crowd. Our Product is High Quality Avery Bubble Free Vinyl material, which is Scratch Proof, Waterproof, Non Fading, Easy To Apply and Remove. It leaves no trace of glue on removing. Skin Lamination is of advanced technology and Matte finish with High Resolution Print Technology. Instructions for Best usage of the Skin : 1. Clean your Laptop surface thoroughly. 2. Take the Measurement of the applying area. 3. Trim the skin to get the exact size. 4. Remove the skin from only one side from the vinyl sheet. 5. Align to the laptop surface and start pressing slowly. 6. After attaching, proceed carefully and press it slightly with the use of a clean cloth or a plastic card to avoid air bubbles and dirt particles.

It differentiates your Laptop from others. A Skin Protects Laptop from outside, adds Aesthetic Appeal and make it Stand Out from the crowd. Our Product is High Quality 3M Avery Bubble Free Vinyl material, which is Scratch Proof, Waterproof, Non Fading, Easy To Apply and Remove. It leaves no trace of glue on removing. Skin Lamination is of advanced technology and Matte finish with High Resolution Print Technology. Instructions for Best usage of the Skin : 1. Clean your Laptop surface thoroughly. 2. Take the Measurement of the applying area. 3. Trim the skin to get the exact size. 4. Remove the skin from only one side from the vinyl sheet. 5. Align to the laptop surface and start pressing slowly. 6. After attaching, proceed carefully and press it slightly with the use of a clean cloth or a plastic card to avoid air bubbles and dirt particles.

It differentiates your Laptop from others. A Skin Protects Laptop from outside, adds Aesthetic Appeal and make it Stand Out from the crowd. Our Product is High Quality 3M Avery Bubble Free Vinyl material, which is Scratch Proof, Waterproof, Non Fading, Easy To Apply and Remove. It leaves no trace of glue on removing. Skin Lamination is of advanced technology and Matte finish with High Resolution Print Technology. Instructions for Best usage of the Skin : 1. Clean your Laptop surface thoroughly. 2. Take the Measurement of the applying area. 3. Trim the skin to get the exact size. 4. Remove the skin from only one side from the vinyl sheet. 5. Align to the laptop surface and start pressing slowly. 6. After attaching, proceed carefully and press it slightly with the use of a clean cloth or a plastic card to avoid air bubbles and dirt particles.
